| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1783 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cc268a84-5204-5cd1-9cc3-168402774f19"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
